            "introduction": {
              "introduction": "　Shim Somi, a passionate new member of Daymine, is a debilitating supporter who disrupts enemy's offensive capabilities.\n\n　When she was working at a call center, she always won the Smile of the Month award. Even after entering the TASKFORCE industry, she never loses her bright smile.\n　Although she makes a lot of mistakes and often gets scolded by her boss, her experience of dealing with terrible customers helps her quickly shake things off and return to work. She has a strong passion for work, but her goal in life is simply to become a proud daughter to her family. "
